data.text: @EJ_Braithwaite Shazam is going to be amazing. I am so excited for this movie. Oh well at least I have the trailer to watch. #shazam https://t.co/tvYgtRWjlY

@markham_therese It is, I wasn’t going to watch after the first trailer. But after this one i am, pee jokes must be DC’s new thing! I now have something else to look forward to while i wait impatiently for Shazam.
@EJ_Braithwaite The trailer is amazing. Nice to see the comic world showing more of a strong female leads.
